            <div class="welovestackoverflow" style="margin-top: 10px;">
                <div style="float: left;">
                        <p>
OTP is the open source distribution of Erlang and an application server written in Erlang. (For the one-time passwords, please use one-time-password tag instead)                         </p>
                                            <p style="margin-bottom: 0;">
                            <a title="tag wiki" href="/tags/otp/info">learn more&hellip;</a>
